					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Note. Number of banks should be a power of 2...<br /><br />1, 2, 4, 8, 16<br /><br />Don't worry about how many banks you need yet. Just stick to NROM128 (Donkey Kong, Pacman) or NROM256 (Super Mario Bros) sized right now.<br /><br />If you have so much code that you overflow past FFFF, the assembler will give you an error. Until that happens, it's not a worry.</div>

					
